# CLI & MCP

## CLI (`packages/cli`)

- Commands: `scan`, `list-scanners`, optional `mcp`
- Delegate to `runScan()` from `core` — no scan logic in CLI
- Exit codes: `0` clean, `1` high/critical findings, `2` runtime error

## MCP (`packages/mcp`)

Tools: `among_check_scan`, `among_check_list_scanners`, `among_check_explain_finding`

- stdio transport default
- Tool schemas must document `ScanTarget` and `ScanOptions` fields
- Stream progress via MCP logging where supported

## Shared rule

Entry surfaces are thin wrappers over `core` + `agents` registry.
